OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of a
OL,6,Ffew showers at first this evening
OL,7,Fotherwise dry. Thickening cloud will
OL,8,Fbring some patchy rain from the west
OL,9,Ffor a time in the early hours.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,12,Ftime in the morning, to leave a mostly
OL,13,Fdry afternoon. Still some patchy rain
OL,14,Facross the Southern Highlands in the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,18,FOutbreaks of rain on Monday morning
OL,19,Fclearing to leave a dry afternoon.
OL,20,FBecoming dry and settled on Tuesday
OL,21,Fand Wednesday with overnight frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
